The probes were purified using the QIAquick PCR purification kit (Qiagen) and quantified using the NanoDrop ND-1000 spectrophotometer (NanoDrop Technologies). The membranes were hybridized overnight at 65 °C in ExpressHyb hybridization solution (Clontech) in a final volume of 20 μl. The membranes were washed twice for 15 min at 65 °C in 2× SSC, 0.1% SDS, and twice for 15 min at 65 °C in 0.1× SSC, 0.1% SDS. The membranes were exposed to a phosphorimager screen for 24 h at −80 °C.
